    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Footed bowls or shallow dishes of varied design used in Greek Orthodox or other Catholic churches to distribute bread that is blessed but not consecrated to those who cannot receive holy communion.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
